      "date": "2012-08-12 17:22:17.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/81c61ec6-e49c-11e1-af05-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  4 tests failed: sanity-quota, conf-sanity, replay-single, sanity.",
