      "date": "2012-09-11 15:44:26.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/96c2e572-fc23-11e1-a4a6-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
